	<div id="c4d-analytics-data" data-title-c4d="AI Agent Frameworks: Choosing the Right Foundation for Your Business" data-last-modified-c4d="Tue Nov 18 12:37:27 UTC 2025" data-last-published-c4d="Tue Nov 18 12:37:27 UTC 2025" data-template-c4d="/conf/adobe-cms-editable/settings/wcm/templates/article-side-navigation" data-playing-mode-c4d="inline">
	</div>


    

</div>

        <h3 class="expressive-heading-03 media-player-ad-video__heading">
            


  
  
    
    Data Insights with LangGraph and watsonx.ai

  





    


        </h3>
        <div class="media-player-ad-video__text">
            
    <span class="  normal cms-richtext">
        <p>Can an AI agent take our natural language query and do the processing for us to give us that meaningful output? We use several pieces of open source technology and the power of watsonx.ai to put this to the test.</p>

    </span>
    
    



        </div>
        <div class="media-player-ad-video__link">

    <!-- NO CARBON -->
    

